profile:
DECKED OUT Vinyl Products Ltd. carries a superior, long lasting and durable vinyl product that is suitable for any climate test.
Whether you choose a traditional or contemporary style you are sure to add beauty and flair to your home or business. 
1. Decked Out gives you the opportunity to buy factory direct, and eliminate the middleman, saving you both time & money!

2. You can come out to the factory and see our professional shop with our custom state-of-the-art manufacturing capabilities.

3. "You fantasize, we will customize" because you are buying directly from the factory, we can custom fabricate your fence.

4. You can install it yourself - vinyl is easier to install and work with than wood!

5. We have a full display in our outdoor and indoor heated showrooms, so that you can look, feel, and touch our products before deciding which way to go.

6. We offer a lifetime warranty on our products against yellowing, peeling, rotting, splintering, rusting or corroding
service_area: Serving Calgary, Red Deer, Lethbridge & surrounding Alberta areas for over 10 years!
